	<div id="bloc-contenu">
		<h5>
    
    
		<a href="http://www.qualitytime-esl.com/spip.php?rubrique37">Free Podcasts</a>
	
	
		<b class='separateur'>&gt;</b> "5 Minute TOPs"
		</h5>
		<div class="ligne-debut"></div><!-- ligne-debut -->
    
    <div class="chapo"><p>Marianne&#8217;s <a href="spip.php?article328" class='spip_in'><strong>5 Minute TOPs</strong></a> are short recordings with exercises that will give you &#8220;Training through Oral Practice&#8221;. The exercises are based on famous quotes or lyrics from well-known songs. Doing these 5-minute exercises either in class, at home or at work will quickly enable you to memorize these structures and make up your own sentences, i.e. express your own ideas. Marianne welcomes suggestions from her listeners for future podcasts.
<span class='spip_document_1020 spip_documents spip_documents_right' style='float:right; width:200px;'>
<img src='IMG/jpg/5_minute_TOPs.jpg' width="200" height="200" alt="" /></span></p>

<p>Marianne&#8217;s book <a href="spip.php?article4" class='spip_in'><strong>QualityTime-ESL: The Digital Resource Book Version 6.0</strong></a> on a <a href="spip.php?article4" class='spip_in'><strong>DVD</strong></a> is available together with our other products in the <a href="http://www.qualitytime-esl.com/store/index.php?page=1&amp;act=viewCat&amp;catId=4" class='spip_out'>store</a>.</p>

